## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="52367-102">提供的內容資訊包含造成引發觸發程序的已修改資料行在更新作業，並在資料定義語言 (DDL) 觸發程序，XML EventData 結構的動作類型 （請參閱 「 TRANSACT-SQL參考 > SQL Server 線上叢書 》 中的），以描述觸發作業。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="52367-102">The contextual information provided includes the type of action that caused the trigger to fire, which columns were modified in an UPDATE operation, and, in the case of a data definition language (DDL) trigger, an XML EventData structure (see "Transact-SQL Reference" in SQL Server Books Online) that describes the triggering operation.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="52367-103">執行個體<xref:Microsoft.SqlServer.Server.SqlTriggerContext>可從<xref:Microsoft.SqlServer.Server.SqlContext>類別，透過觸發程序內執行程式碼時<xref:Microsoft.SqlServer.Server.SqlContext.TriggerContext%2A>屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="52367-103">An instance of <xref:Microsoft.SqlServer.Server.SqlTriggerContext> is available from the <xref:Microsoft.SqlServer.Server.SqlContext> class, when the code is running inside a trigger through the <xref:Microsoft.SqlServer.Server.SqlContext.TriggerContext%2A> property.</span></span>  
  
   
  
